#

Caprese Tomato Toast

15 min
$8.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

QuickEasyLight Meal

Description

A refreshing and simple toast topped with juicy tomatoes, creamy mozzarella, and fragrant basil, perfect for a quick snack or light meal.

Ingredients

  • sourdough bread: 2 slices
  • fresh mozzarella: 100 grams
  • ripe tomatoes: 2 medium
  • fresh basil leaves: a handful
  • balsamic glaze: to drizzle
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
